<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Computer Vision | Liu Yue — Embodied AI Researcher</title><link>https://miracle-techlink.github.io/vivid-aurora-space/tags/computer-vision/</link><atom:link href="https://miracle-techlink.github.io/vivid-aurora-space/tags/computer-vision/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><description>Computer Vision</description><generator>Hugo Blox Builder (https://hugoblox.com)</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><image><url>https://miracle-techlink.github.io/vivid-aurora-space/media/icon_hu_982c5d63a71b2961.png</url><title>Computer Vision</title><link>https://miracle-techlink.github.io/vivid-aurora-space/tags/computer-vision/</link></image><item><title>AGV Reception &amp; Inspection Robot — Tongji Deployment</title><link>https://miracle-techlink.github.io/vivid-aurora-space/projects/agv-reception/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://miracle-techlink.github.io/vivid-aurora-space/projects/agv-reception/</guid><description>&lt;p>Participated in the R&amp;amp;D of an intelligent AGV robot platform deployed across Tongji University&amp;rsquo;s exhibition hall and teaching buildings. The system integrates two robot roles — &lt;strong>reception (迎宾)&lt;/strong> and &lt;strong>inspection (巡检)&lt;/strong> — on a shared AGV chassis with a modular AI brain architecture.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>My contribution:&lt;/strong> Led the &lt;strong>voice module localization for Middle East clients&lt;/strong> — adapting the NLP pipeline for Arabic speech recognition, TTS, and interaction flows to support overseas commercial deployment.&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;h3 id="deployment">Deployment&lt;/h3>
&lt;figure>&lt;img src="https://miracle-techlink.github.io/vivid-aurora-space/projects/agv-reception/featured.jpg"
alt="Left: Reception robot in Tongji University Exhibition Hall. Right: Inspection robot in Tongji teaching building.">&lt;figcaption>
&lt;p>Left: Reception robot in Tongji University Exhibition Hall. Right: Inspection robot in Tongji teaching building.&lt;/p>
&lt;/figcaption>
&lt;/figure>
&lt;hr>
&lt;h3 id="system-architecture">System Architecture&lt;/h3>
&lt;figure>&lt;img src="https://miracle-techlink.github.io/vivid-aurora-space/projects/agv-reception/arch.png"
alt="Dual-brain architecture: AI大脑 (data analysis / model inference / HRI) &amp;#43; AGV大脑 (autonomous navigation controller) on a unified AGV platform.">&lt;figcaption>
&lt;p>Dual-brain architecture: AI大脑 (data analysis / model inference / HRI) + AGV大脑 (autonomous navigation controller) on a unified AGV platform.&lt;/p>
&lt;/figcaption>
&lt;/figure>
&lt;p>The robot uses a &lt;strong>dual-brain architecture&lt;/strong>:&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>AI 大脑&lt;/strong> — handles 数据分析, 模型推理, 人机交互 (vision, NLP, multimodal interaction)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>AGV 大脑&lt;/strong> — autonomous navigation controller (SLAM, path planning, motor control)&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;hr>
